== Russian ==
=== Etymology ===
[[тусовать]] + [[-щик]]

=== Noun ===
'''тусо́вщик''' (tusóvščik) {{m}}; [[agent noun]] from [[тусовать]]

# {{italbrac|slang}} a [[club kid]], a person who often attends [[hangout]]s, especially teenager’s hangouts
# {{italbrac|slang|figurative}} a person who is a member of a [[coterie]]

